%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'primaryColor': '#4A90D9', 'primaryTextColor': '#fff', 'lineColor': '#333'}}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[🔴 Payment fails] --> B[Enter dunning state]
    B --> C[Set subscription status: PastDue]
    C --> D[Classify decline code]

    D --> E{Decline category}
    E -->|Transient error| F[Retry in 1 hour]
    E -->|Insufficient funds| G[Retry in 3 days]
    E -->|Card expired| H[Send update card email\nRetry after 7 days]
    E -->|Hard decline\nDo not honor| I[Flag for manual review]
    E -->|Card blocked\nFraud| J[Do not retry\nSuspend immediately]

    F --> K{Retry succeeds?}
    G --> K
    H --> K

    K -->|Yes| L[✅ Payment recovered]
    L --> M[Status → Active]
    M --> N[Send recovery confirmation]

    K -->|No| O{Attempts remaining?}
    O -->|Yes| P[Schedule next retry\nwith backoff]
    P --> Q[Send dunning email\nDay 3 / 7 / 14]
    Q --> K

    O -->|No| R[Max retries exhausted]
    R --> S[Send final notice email]
    S --> T{Grace period active?}
    T -->|Yes| U[Suspend access\nbut keep subscription]
    T -->|No| V[❌ Cancel subscription]
    U --> W[Wait for customer action]
    W -->|Customer updates card| K
    W -->|Grace period expires| V
    V --> X[Involuntary churn recorded]

    style A fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style L fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
    style V fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style M fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
